author: Business Insider
description:
After scaling peaks around the world, L. Renee Blount sets her sights on skiing some of Colorado’s most famous mountains.

From mastering ski techniques at Copper Mountain to exploring some of Vail's must-visit spots, join L. as she embraces Vail’s winter spirit in this episode of “Connected Journeys.”

Find out more about the places featured in L.’s story:

The Hythe, a Luxury Collection Resort, Vail: https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/egelc-the-hythe-a-luxury-collection-resort-vail/overview/
Copper Mountain: https://www.coppercolorado.com/
Root & Flower: https://www.rootandflowervail.com/
Colorado Snowsports Museum & Hall of Fame: https://www.snowsportsmuseum.org/
The Well & Being Spa: https://na.spatime.com/egelc/11327942/home
Revel Lounge: https://www.thehythevail.com/dining/revel-lounge/
